PrecisAppointment of KAREN SUE BRENNAN, of Oshawa, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Canada Industrial Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years; and order that KAREN SUE BRENNAN be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act, effective February 15, 1999.
